	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum tuae mihi adferrentur, non eram domi, sed paululum rus abieram.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellum meum, quem tibi mutuo dederam, accepi; accepi et tumultus <placeName type="auto_name">Ambosiani</placeName> historiam, pro qua gratias ago tuae humanitati.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Becoini collation cum acceperis, rem facies gratissimam, si communicaveris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exemplum supplicationis <persName type="auto_name">Ihenensium</persName>, cui se subscripserunt <placeName type="auto_name">Roth</placeName> et <placeName type="auto_name">Neckar</placeName>, mali vicini et male feriati homines, qui se honestius turbulentis illis non miscuissent, habes hic, sed ea lege, ut remittas mature et tuto per proximum tabellionem, non tamen prius, quam illo abunde usus es.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nova nunc habemus nulla, nisi quod fama subinde increscit <placeName type="auto_name">Leytham</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotia</placeName> captam ab <placeName type="auto_name">Anglis</placeName> et <placeName type="auto_name">Gallos</placeName> omnes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotia</placeName> esse eiectos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego tamen hoc nondum pro certo affirmare ausim; ubi certiora habuero, communicabo.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name">7 Cantones</placeName> festinarunt in <placeName type="auto_name">Valesiam</placeName>; legatos intelligo missos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non habet hodie infensiores hostes evangelium Christi per Europam quam Quinque illos Pagicos, quibus se iungunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l160">Friburgenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Solodorii</placeName>; libenter ad se raperent et <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronenses</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vehementer crescit in <placeName type="auto_name">Valesia</placeName> fidelium numerus; putant ergo hostes illi Christi in tempore praeveniendum, ne tandem nimis sero velint factum, quod nunc moliuntur.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed vivit, qui omnes mundi persequtores attrivit; atterat ergo et hos aut benigne convertat ad ipsum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miserunt et <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernenses</placeName> suos legatos, sed dubito, num satis in tempore.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> spargunt rumores novos subinde exoriri contra <persName type="auto_name">Guysianos</persName> tumultus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concilium redintegrare cogitat papa; nunc illi certamen est cum <persName type="auto_name">Carachis</persName>, quos omnes prope in carceres coniecit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Parat sibi undique hostes, ne regnum eius <foreign xml:lang="de">in aller tüfel namen</foreign> sit diuturnum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus deus noster liberet nos ab istis diabolis et belluis.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale aeternum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName> 27. iulii 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvus sit noster <persName type="auto_name">Matthias</persName> et alii viri boni etc.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sinem fürgeliebten herren und bruͦder m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName>, diser zyt zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Wintherdur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
